      "value": "<h3 id=\"HippieDragonReferences-ReferenceBoard\">Reference Board</h3><p>The first step of starting any new project is to collect references as this is one step that is equally important as proper texturing or lookdev, if not more. I gathered references for different materials and also some images I took as inspiration and compiled them in a reference board with the help of a software named Pureref. Here is a glimpse of some of my main references.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image9.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657162426/image9.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592499672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=454\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657162426/image9.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592499672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"969\" data-width=\"1621\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657228077\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image9.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657162426\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"34aed66f-948d-4156-a11f-980d77f533c6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657162426/image9.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592499672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=908 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657162426/image9.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592499672&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=454 1x\"></span><p />"
